l style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">Patrick O&#=
8217;Shaughnessy</a><span> on </span><em>Invest Like the Best. </em></p><p =
style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>In recent years, he&#8217;s used the podcast circuit t=
o go scorched-earth on the investors, partners, and journalists that he bel=
ieves mistreated him earlier in his career. You should go find those podcas=
